OL,3,CNHS staff so 'embarrassed' by corridor
OL,4,Ccare they avoid eye contact with
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FNHS staff are avoiding eye contact
OL,8,Fwith patients because they are so
OL,9,F"embarrassed" about corridor care in
OL,10,Fhospitals, MPs have been told.
OL,12,FIt comes as a new poll found half of
OL,13,Femergency care senior doctors feel
OL,14,Ftheir A&E department is "unsafe" for
OL,15,Fpatients.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@MO]vD@YOUvD@`O]
