OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773280992
OL,3,CNHS staff so 'embarrassed' by corridor
OL,4,Ccare they avoid eye contact with
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FMPs on the Health Select Committee
OL,8,Fhave questioned the Health Minister
OL,9,Fand NHS England bosses about the
OL,10,Fgrowing problem of patients being
OL,11,Ftreated on trolleys and chairs in
OL,12,Fcorridors, or in areas not designed to
OL,13,Fbe clinical spaces.
OL,15,FIn recent months, ITV News has been
OL,16,Finvestigating the issue, with secretly
OL,17,Ffilmed footage exposing "war zone"
OL,18,Fconditions in some hospitals.
OL,26,@yD@YOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773280992
OL,3,CNHS staff so 'embarrassed' by corridor
OL,4,Ccare they avoid eye contact with
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FDuring today's evidence, the chair of
OL,8,Fthe committee, Layla Moran MP,
OL,9,Freferred to ITV News' reporting,
OL,10,Fquoting our interviews with patients
OL,11,Fwho've experienced the "mental
OL,12,Fcruelty" of corridor care.
OL,14,FIn response, the Health Minister Karin
OL,15,FSmyth told the committee it was
OL,16,F"unacceptable" for patients and
OL,17,F"awful" for staff.
OL,26,@sD@XOUtD@HO]xD@AOUxD@NO]yD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773280992
OL,3,CNHS staff so 'embarrassed' by corridor
OL,4,Ccare they avoid eye contact with
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,F"We are absolutely, very clear that
OL,8,Fthis is unacceptable, that the phrase
OL,9,F'normalised' is not normalised, and
OL,10,Fthat is why the Secretary of State
OL,11,Fcommitted to see the end of that
OL,12,Fpractice by the end of the current
OL,13,FParliament." She told MPs.
OL,15,F"I think the definition, and indeed
OL,16,Fthe collection, and the publication of
OL,17,Fdata, are also a key part of
OL,18,Fdemonstrating that commitment and
OL,19,Fmaking sure that we get that right."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@LO]wD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
