CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773280992
OL,3,CNHS staff so 'embarrassed' by corridor
OL,4,Ccare they avoid eye contact with
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FProfessor Nicola Ranger, chief
OL,8,Fexecutive and general secretary of the
OL,9,FRoyal College of Nursing, told MPs
OL,10,Fthat many nurses feel "ashamed" of
OL,11,Fcurrent conditions in A&E departments.
OL,13,FProfessor Ranger described the
OL,14,Fsituation as an "emergency" with many
OL,15,Fnurses "losing hope".
OL,17,F"They feel embarrassed, so there's a
OL,18,Flack of eye contact," she told the
OL,19,Fcommittee.
OL,26,@rD@WOUrD@_O]vD@QOUvD@[O]wD@HOUwD@TO]yD@
OL,26,AAOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
