PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773280992
OL,3,CNHS staff so 'embarrassed' by corridor
OL,4,Ccare they avoid eye contact with
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,F"Those are symptoms of people just
OL,8,F'head down' because they feel upset
OL,9,Fwith what they're seeing.
OL,11,F"And when patients are struggling for
OL,12,Fa nurse to give them eye contact,
OL,13,Fthat's not a good place... I think
OL,14,Fthat's a real symptom of many nurses
OL,15,Fnot feeling proud of what they are
OL,16,Fdoing."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
