OL,3,CNHS staff so 'embarrassed' by corridor
OL,4,Ccare they avoid eye contact with
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FMPs heard that one emergency
OL,8,Fdepartment consultant told a colleague
OL,9,Fthat he couldn't work another shift,
OL,10,Fbecause he was "embarrassed at the
OL,11,Fcare we are delivering."
OL,13,FDr Ian Higginson, president of the
OL,14,FRoyal College of Emergency Medicine,
OL,15,Frevealed a new poll of emergency
OL,16,Fmedicine clinical leaders, in which
OL,17,Fhalf (51%)of respondents said their
OL,18,Femergency department was "fairly or
OL,19,Fvery unsafe".
OL,26,@rD@POUsD@XO]zD@ZOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
