PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773280992
OL,3,CNHS staff so 'embarrassed' by corridor
OL,4,Ccare they avoid eye contact with
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FThe survey of leaders in 80 of
OL,8,FEngland's emergency departments also
OL,9,Ffound:
OL,11,FNHS England is due to start publishing
OL,12,Fthe data on corridor care by May 2026.
OL,14,FThe government has committed to ending
OL,15,Fall corridor care by the end of the
OL,16,FParliament, thought to be in 2029.
